---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Τα Έργα μας" active="projects">

<main class="pt-32 pb-24 max-w-[1440px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">
  <header class="mb-24">
    <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 mb-6">
      <div class="h-px w-12 bg-primary"></div>
      <span class="text-primary font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.4em]">Our Work</span>
    </div>
    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black italic mb-8 uppercase">
      PROJECT <span class="text-primary">PORTFOLIO</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-text-muted max-w-2xl leading-relaxed font-medium">
      Εξερευνήστε τις πρόσφατες υλοποιήσεις μας σε βιομηχανικές και μεταλλικές κατασκευές.
    </p>
  </header>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
    <a href="/projects/steel-roof" class="group relative aspect-video overflow-hidden border border-border/50">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1541888946425-d81bb19240f5?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Steel Roof" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700" />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-background/60 flex flex-col justify-end p-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-black italic uppercase text-white mb-2">Steel Roof Structure</h2>
        <p class="text-primary font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs">Industrial Fabrication</p>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/projects/industrial-walkway" class="group relative aspect-video overflow-hidden border border-border/50">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1513828583688-c52646db42da?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Industrial Walkway" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700" />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-background/60 flex flex-col justify-end p-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-black italic uppercase text-white mb-2">Industrial Walkway</h2>
        <p class="text-primary font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs">Custom Engineering</p>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/projects/custom-fabrications" class="group relative aspect-video overflow-hidden border border-border/50">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1565615833231-e8c91a38a012?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Custom Fab" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700" />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-background/60 flex flex-col justify-end p-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-black italic uppercase text-white mb-2">Custom Fabrications</h2>
        <p class="text-primary font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs">Automotive Industry</p>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/projects/precision-welding" class="group relative aspect-video overflow-hidden border border-border/50">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1531986346396-672440560981?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Welding" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700" />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-background/60 flex flex-col justify-end p-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-black italic uppercase text-white mb-2">Precision Welding</h2>
        <p class="text-primary font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs">Technical Services</p>
      </div>
    </a>
  </div>
</main>

</Layout>
